Uses of Interface
com.joliciel.talismane.utils.io.CurrentFileObserver

  • Packages that use CurrentFileObserver 
    Package Description
    com.joliciel.talismane.corpus
    A package dealing with reading annotated corpora.
    com.joliciel.talismane.extensions.standoff
    A package for converting to and from CoNLL-X to standoff format, for interaction with annoation tools requiring this format.
    com.joliciel.talismane.parser
    Transition-based dependency parsing ( Parser) and output artefacts ( ParseConfiguration, ParseTree, and DependencyNode).
    com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger
    Package enabling the part-of-speech tagging of a TokenSequence.
    The central class is the PosTagger.
    com.joliciel.talismane.rawText
    Package managing the initial filtering of an input stream, such as in the case of XML analysis, where the XML tags need to be removed, and in some case represent sentence breaks.
    com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser
    Tokenisation package.
    com.joliciel.talismane.utils.io
    Various I/O utilities.

      Writes standoff annotations readable by the Brat annotation tool: see http://brat.nlplab.org/ To be useable by Brat, these need to be accompanied in the same directory by sentences written using the StandoffSentenceWriter.

    • Uses of CurrentFileObserver in com.joliciel.talismane.parser

      Classes in com.joliciel.talismane.parser that implement CurrentFileObserver 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ParserRegexBasedCorpusReader
      A corpus reader that expects one pos-tagged token with dependency info per line, and analyses the line content based on a regex supplied during construction, via a CorpusLineReader.
      The following placeholders are required:
      CorpusLine.CorpusElement.INDEX, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.TOKEN, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.POSTAG, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.LABEL, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.GOVERNOR.

    • Uses of CurrentFileObserver in com.joliciel.talismane.rawText
